27:15.133 --> 27:16.533
Yeah!

27:16.600 --> 27:17.866
They guy with..

27:17.933 --> 27:19.100
...with the gun!

27:19.166 --> 27:20.433
You're good.

27:20.500 --> 27:21.833
Realgood.

27:25.300 --> 27:27.133
