there's another guy.

27:27.200 --> 27:28.166
Oh, but there was.

27:28.233 --> 27:29.400
- Smoke?
- No.

27:29.466 --> 27:31.466
I-I-I quit.

27:31.533 --> 27:33.833
Of course.

27:33.900 --> 27:36.566
Always the same story
with your type.

27:36.633 --> 27:39.066
Blame somebody else
for your situation.

27:39.133 --> 27:41.300
What situation?
