32:36.233 --> 32:38.466
Uh, look.

32:38.533 --> 32:40.000
Cindy, I know we had
a fight this morning

32:40.066 --> 32:41.533
but this is getting
so ridiculous.

32:41.600 --> 32:43.166
Get out of here.
Go away.

32:43.233 --> 32:45.700
I'm not going anywhere.

32:45.766 --> 32:47.200
This is my house.

32:47.266 --> 32:48.933
I need help.

32:49.000 --> 32:51.300
You're bothering
my wife and kid?

32:53.366 --> 32:56.133
Your wife and kid?

32:56.833 --> 32:57.966
Take a hike.

33:03.066 --> 33:04.733
Pretty please.

33:07.700 --> 33:09.033
You're that guy.

33:11.266 --> 33:13.233
You're that guy!

33:22.966 --> 33:25.033
Ready when you are, Vinny.

33:33.033 --> 33:35.000
Where are we now?

33:36.800 --> 33:39.433
Where do you think?

33:39.500 --> 33:41.433
Well, surprise me.

33:42.533 --> 33:44.600
Come on, Vinny.
This is your house.

33:45.733 --> 33:47.800
This is your empire.
You built this.

33:50.100 --> 33:54.000
Oh. Who is Vinny?

33:58.700 --> 33:59.733
Vinny?

34:06.333 --> 34:07.733
My lover.

34:26.033 --> 34:27.200
Hey!

34:28.600 --> 34:29.700
My keys.

34:30.766 --> 34:32.066
Yeah.

34:32.133 --> 34:33.666
You left them here
this morning.

34:33.733 --> 34:35.900
You left your wallet too.

34:37.666 --> 34:39.300
They're over here.

34:58.900 --> 35:00.533
These are my clothes.

35:00.600 --> 35:02.733
'What did you expect?'

35:06.700 --> 35:08.633
I don't know what to expect.

35:09.466 --> 35:11.333
I've misplaced my life.

35:12.166 --> 35:14.366
Oh. Cheer up.

35:14.433 --> 35:16.933
You don't need
to expect anything.

35:17.000 --> 35:19.066
That's what I love about you.

35:19.133 --> 35:20.366
You're so..

35:20.433 --> 35:22.633
...um, so spontaneous.

35:22.700 --> 35:24.500
Mr. Adventure.

35:25.600 --> 35:27.066
Uh, those pictures downstairs.

35:27.133 --> 35:29.333
I-I looked happy in them.
Was I happy when we took 'em?

35:29.400 --> 35:31.566
Oh, yeah.
Oh, you were very happy.

35:31.633 --> 35:34.066
You had just hit a big score.

35:34.133 --> 35:36.666
We were sailing off the Keys.

35:38.200 --> 35:40.233
And then, then you said
that your wife and kids

35:40.300 --> 35:42.366
were suckers.

35:42.433 --> 35:44.766
You haven't changed
your mind, have you?

35:44.833 --> 35:46.033
No.

35:46.100 --> 35:48.133
No, I haven't changed it.

35:49.233 --> 35:51.200
I've just lost it.

35:51.266 --> 35:52.333
Completely.

35:58.433 --> 36:00.433
Hey, this is mine.

36:01.400 --> 36:02.466
Information's all wrong though.

36:02.533 --> 36:05.033
It's...wrong address.

36:06.200 --> 36:08.200
Not if it's this address, babe.

36:15.633 --> 36:17.700
Oh.

36:17.766 --> 36:19.366
Sorry about your headphones,
but I told you

36:19.433 --> 36:20.566
not to put them
next to the bed

36:20.633 --> 36:25.000
especially because you
get so rough

36:25.066 --> 36:27.033
when it comes time
for bedtime.

36:27.666 --> 36:29.233
Me? Rough?

36:29.300 --> 36:32.233
Mm-hmm. You're an animal.

36:32.300 --> 36:34.033
Sexual beast.

36:34.833 --> 36:37.100
Oh.

36:37.166 --> 36:40.200
My poor little gem of a baby.

36:40.266 --> 36:42.733
You just get into
too much too soon.

36:44.166 --> 36:45.800
Yeah, I never thought
anything exciting

36:45.866 --> 36:47.833
would ever happen to me.

36:47.900 --> 36:49.866
I thought I'll just turn 50

36:49.933 --> 36:52.933
and...it'd be all over.

36:53.000 --> 36:55.900
Well, you don't have to worry
about that happening to you now.

36:58.633 --> 37:01.900
Because you're in all the way.

37:01.966 --> 37:04.100
It doesn't matter if you're in
all the way if you're lost.

37:04.166 --> 37:08.000
Well, then let me help you
out of the woods.

37:08.066 --> 37:09.500
Alright.

37:22.533 --> 37:24.500
He's all yours.

37:24.566 --> 37:27.033
Humped, primed and ready.

37:29.133 --> 37:30.333
Take him.

38:19.166 --> 38:21.100
Well, that was fast.

38:22.300 --> 38:24.533
I told you his kind
wouldn't be any trouble.

38:26.066 --> 38:27.433
He wasn't.

38:38.366 --> 38:40.533
I'm beginning to catch on
with my new life.

38:40.600 --> 38:43.266
You think I like the feeling
of this weapon in my hand?

38:43.333 --> 38:44.733
So don't do that again.

38:44.800 --> 38:47.000
Just let me go!

38:47.066 --> 38:49.066
I want answers.

38:49.133 --> 38:50.100
Now..

38:51.800 --> 38:53.366
...who are you?

38:53.433 --> 38:55.100
What's happening to me?

38:55.166 --> 38:56.300
Who's doing this?

38:56.366 --> 38:58.400
You did it to yourself.

38:59.566 --> 39:01.266
Who's life am I living?

39:01.333 --> 39:02.600
This isn't me.

39:02.666 --> 39:04.033
It's not my life.

39:04.100 --> 39:06.533
Don't you get it?

39:07.500 --> 39:09.800
You've made Vinny what he is.

39:09.866 --> 39:12.000
You made him up!

39:22.300 --> 39:23.933
Well, I-I-I was just 40 and I..

39:25.233 --> 39:27.733
I was p-pushing 40.

39:27.800 --> 39:31.100
I just, you know,
felt like I was in a rud.

39:31.166 --> 39:32.400
