39:32.466 --> 39:35.100
So, I was.. So I'm supposed
to die for it?

39:40.200 --> 39:42.200
They're all over the place.

39:42.966 --> 39:44.566
What have you done to me?

39:44.633 --> 39:47.200
'Ready, guys. Spread out.
Keep your eyes open.'

39:47.866 --> 39:49.100
Alright.

39:51.600 --> 39:53.500
You want out. You can get out.

39:53.566 --> 39:55.966
