It's all your choice.

39:56.033 --> 39:57.366
'Look in here.'

39:59.433 --> 40:00.833
Right here.

40:02.466 --> 40:03.833
Keys to my car.

40:05.333 --> 40:07.400
Why should I trust you?

40:10.266 --> 40:11.400
Yeah?

40:11.466 --> 40:15.000
